        <updateDate>2022-09-09T20:53:49Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Terminating Reckless and Unnecessary Checks Known to Erode Regular Shipping Act or the TRUCKERS Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the Department of Homeland Security from imposing any COVID-19 vaccination requirement on any commercial truck driver who is a national of Canada or Mexico and seeking to temporarily enter the United States for business through a land port of entry. <br> </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
